<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    After Alexis, Mercedes, and Porsche were taken by CPS, the twins were adopted by Midnight. He also tried to adopt Porsche, but he could not locate her<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    After Alexis, Mercedes, and Porsche were taken by CPS, the twins were adopted by Midnight. He also tried to adopt Porsche, but he could not locate her. She was transferred to a youth detention facility were she linked up with a group of young ladies, and they put together an escape plan. Once Porsche escaped, she went back to NY to find her mother, who lost everything and became a drug addict. Porsche worked odd jobs to support herself and try to heal her mother. During this time she met a young man who later became a big time movie director, they married, she became pregnant, and had their first child.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
