              <span id="reviewTextContainer53387268" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15343589368492091585">I could not put this book down, no matter what was going on around me. This world was far from my world, yet it was so real. How long does it take to learn a lesson?</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

